      <h2>Preparation</h2>
      <section>
        <h3>Objectives</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>The student will model multiplication and division of integers (with the same sign and different signs) using two-colored counters, a two-sided mat, and a number line.</li>
          <li>The student will evaluate the product and quotient of two integers, with the same sign or different signs.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h3>Essential Questions</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>How do I multiply integers?</li>
          <li>Why does <span class="js-mt">(-1)(-1)=1</span>?</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h3>Vocabulary</h3>
        <dl class="vocablist">
          <dt>product</dt>
          <dd>the answer to a multiplication problem</dd>
          <dt>quotient</dt>
          <dd>the answer to a division problem</dd>
